# Walmart recording

- Manual research only — no auto-checkout, no Discord link opening.
- One global recording session across all Walmart tabs; content batches via `WALMART_RECORDING_APPEND`.
- Content never writes IndexedDB directly — background handlers persist via IDB lib.
- Inject research probe only while recording (`page-probe-bridge.ts`).
- Export mutex (`tryAcquireExport`) — tab-close and stop share pipeline.
- Handlers split under `background/handlers/` — extend existing modules, do not merge into monolith.

See `extension/domains/walmart/AGENTS.md` and `extension/domains/walmart/docs/WALMART_RECORDING.md`.
